information: EL NOGAL, founded in 1980 in Campo Lameiro (Spain), is a company that specialises in the sale of high quality nuts and dried fruit. With its 45-strong team working from a 5.000 m² facility, EL NOGAL has a production capacity of 4, 500 tonnes and it can be found at the leading trade shows. Our main customers are supermarket chains such as Carrefour, Leclerc and Auchan, who choose to work with us because they know that we are a supplier they can rely on.
